          "text": "int isqrt(int n)\n{\n\tint x;\n\tint x1;\n\n\tif (n < 1) {\n\t\tx = 0;\n\t} else if (n == 1) {\n\t\tx = 1;\n\t} else {\n\t\tx = n;\n\t\tx1 = (x + 1) / 2;\n\t\twhile (x1 < x) {\n\t\t\tx = x1;\n\t\t\tx1 = (x1 + n / x1) / 2;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\treturn x;\n}",
